      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "content": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "The Entra Verified ID issuance and verification flows share a common structure: your app calls the Request Service API, receives a QR code, displays it to the user, and handles the outcome via a webhook callback."
          }
        ]
      },
